channel.title: Rs3 Revolution Pkz-Anti silab**Now hiring**
channel.description:
Hello Moparscape,I'm bringing back my old server and decided to make rs3 revolution-This time a pk server with some non combat skills as well,I don't want it to be silabs-God knows when the item id's will change and things will fuck up/glitch.My first Normal Mopar server lol,Anyways Below is info on joining and other info. What will the server include? I want the server to be dedicated to pking,So basically Train then pk,Maybe add some non combat skills(Doubt it).I also want it to be a minigame server,such as barrows pc and other fun things that are like pking but you can be on teams with players-Also want to add castle wars.I don't want a lot of commands,and I want a small client.java because more kb/mb in client.java the more lag you will have,and if it's a pk server you can't have much lag. What will the server base be? It will be from the Original Rs3 revolution-Non pkz Made by me (rs w00dcut) I really don't want to add a lot of commands,I'd love to remove a lot of commands and make just pk & Pots/Food commands and things like that,I'll be working with adding commands,Shops,removing stuff out of client.java,I will only accept people with Aim &/Or Msn-For sending files and shit.Yes, i've changed my mine-I don't want any non Combat skills and if I find any I will most likely Remove them.I will try to make this server as real as possible.I want this to be a stable server,So i'm adding Syipkpker protection and other Hacker & Cheat client Protections.
[b]Things to be accomplished:[/b]
[ul][li]Make forums-So other members on the project can chat freely about it[/li] [li]Want to edit all the shops and make into all pking & armor & weapons.[/li][/ul]
[ul][li]Add minigames(I.e.,Barrows,Castlewars etc)[/li] [li]Want to add new pk areas-As well as pk boxes and other things[/li][/ul]
[ul][li]Remove alot of shit from client.java that is not needed[/li] [li]Want to add tons of Handlers[/li][/ul]
[ul][li]Add Food timers and other things[/li] [li]Add Protection from Cheatclients & Other hackers.[/li][/ul]
[b]Accomplished:[/b]
[ul][li]Nothing;lol[/li][/ul]
[b]Jobs Open:[/b]
[ul][li]Forum Moderator[/li] [li]Idea Developers[/li][/ul]
[b]Applications:[/b] [code]Position Wanted- Experience- Proof(Links)*Must have* Msn*Must have*- Aim- Email- How many days a week are you on the computer- How many hours a day are you on the computer- Can you Send & Download/Receive Files- How long have you been dealing with Moparscape- Proof*Must have*- Will you obey all rules no Matter what- Are you reliable- How creative are you-[/code]
[center][b]Staff List & People on the job:[/b][/center]
[center]Main Programmers(Objects,autospawn,Npcs,shops etc.) [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php?action=profile;u=165816]Xx qwertyuiop xx[/url] [/center] [center]Forum Developer: [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php?action=profile;u=115606]itzkyle[/url] [/center]
